 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"就算冇削骨點都有做手腳<br />\n打死唔信減肥減到塊面瘦成個碼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T23:20:19.000Z","msg":"佢以前包包面架<br />\n後尾要出caffiene 操fit 咗個人<br />\n先顯到下巴咁尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8de4dc772d820ec00305cc7d1932a2dc6441e27","tid":570962,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.kpopn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/20180228_yoseob.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kpopn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2F20180228_yoseob.jpg&h=b4cc273d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHIGHLIGHT 耀燮以新曲《Where I Am Gone》獲得本週 (27日) SBS MTV《THE SHOW》冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n《THE SHOW》透過官方推特分享耀燮一位認證照，表示：「第138集 THE SHOW Choice 主角是？恭~喜~#舞情曲 (即搭配舞蹈的抒情曲) 的王者 #梁耀燮，祝賀獲得 THE SHOW Choice！Bba Baam！(原文：138회 더쇼 초이스 주인공은? 콩~그~레~츄~레이션~#댄라드 의 #왕자 #양요섭 더쇼 초이스의 수상을 축하합니다! 뺘뱜!!)」。<br />\n<br />\n這是耀燮久違地 SOLO 回歸後獲得的首個一位，他不只感謝公司 Aroud Us Entertainment、HIGHLIGHT 成員與粉絲們，還為了紀念獲得一位、謝謝粉絲們的支持，特地公開小小的禮物 ─《Wher I Am Gone》舞蹈練習版送給 LIGHT (粉絲名)。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.kpopn.com/2018/02/28/耀燮新曲《where-gone》獲本週《the-show》冠軍！/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kpopn.com%2F2018%2F02%2F28%2F%E8%80%80%E7%87%AE%E6%96%B0%E6%9B%B2%E3%80%8Awhere-gone%E3%80%8B%E7%8D%B2%E6%9C%AC%E9%80%B1%E3%80%8Athe-show%E3%80%8B%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D%EF%BC%81%2F&d=ZSUkDF0cKWt9FWKYi9HxhjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b2d898e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kpopn.com/2018/02/28/耀燮新曲《where-gone》獲本週《the-show》冠軍！/</a>"},{"pid":"9d5eb736478a26d54d5e1c92590b1c06fae1f311","tid":570962,"uid":64699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:32:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eede876f4c16527a0453c159ba2bef76a622d688","tid":570962,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d5eb736478a26d54d5e1c92590b1c06fa